  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r6/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md` and locate tasks 089 + 090. Record their status symbols.</step>
    <step order="2">Run `gh pr view 401 --json state,title,mergeable,statusCheckRollup` to capture R6 hotfix PR status.</step>
    <step order="3">Run `git log --oneline -n 20 master` (or `origin/master`) to check whether R6 closeout commits have landed.</step>
    <step order="4">Inspect any R6 UAT regression evidence — typically `projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r6/notes/uat/` or PR #401 description.</step>
    <step order="5">Create `projects/spaarke-ai-platform-chat-routing-redesign-r1/notes/handoffs/000-r6-readiness-confirmation.md` summarizing findings. Mark GO / NO-GO.</step>
    <step order="6">If NO-GO: update `current-task.md` with blocker; escalate to owner. If GO: update TASK-INDEX task 000 → ✅; current-task.md → ready for wave 0-A.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
